textBeforeTable: Music Read the full recap Recap The episode begins at a bachelorette party. After the party, the bride-to-be and her friends head to another bar. They run into another car. They then see two men get down from the other car, open the trunk of their car, fire shots and then run away. They are horror struck when they see the dead body in the trunk. Next, Steve arrives to meet Mick Logan, ex-military intelligence. He wants Mick to investigate his mother, Doris. Steve tells him that Doris is a former Government agent. He wants to know what his mother is up to. Steve gets a call. Later, at the HQ, Kono briefs the team about the victim. His name is Thomas Hoapili and he has a daughter, Maggie Hoapili. ..
